  "Nested functions like sin(cos(x^2)) have multiple layers of composition. Each layer requires its own application of the chain rule, differentiating from the outside in.": "诸如罪(cos(x% 2)) 等内脏函数具有多层构成。 每一层都需要自己应用链条规则, 与外层不同 。",
  "What does 'substitution' mean when applying the chain rule?": "在适用链条规则时,“替代”意味着什么?",
  "Removing the inner function entirely": "完全删除内部函数",
