  "Letting u equal the inner function to simplify the differentiation process": "让内功能等同内功能以简化差异化程序",
  "u-substitution in the chain rule means letting u = g(x) (the inner function). Then y = f(u), dy/dx = dy/du * du/dx. This breaks a complex derivative into simpler steps.": "u- 在链条规则中的替代意味着让 u = g(x) (内部函数) 。 y = f( u), dy/ dx = dy/ du * du/ dx 。 这将复杂的衍生物分成更简单的步骤 。",
  "What is the 'generalized power rule'?": "什么是“普遍权力规则”?",
  "d/dx[f(x)]^n = n[f(x)]^(n-1) * f'(x)": "d/dx[f(x)]}n = n[f(x)]}}(n-1) * f'(x) = n[f(x)]}(n-1) * f'(x)",
